msgstr "Traduction et autres contributions au projet Slint"

#. type: Plain text
#: HandBook.adoc:82
msgid "Slint need translators! If you want to participate to the translation effort, read the instructions in https://slint.fr/doc/translate_slint.html[Translate Slint]."
